      <talk_answer link_index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-a" mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Court Sorceress Kayleen$<BR>I am one of the best Sorceress in Saint Haven. Although I didn’t officially take on the Dark Tower name, I was one of the students that Master Karacule approved of. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-b" mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>You should consider your age.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-d" mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>Wake up!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-g" mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>It's good to have a dream.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Court Sorceress Kayleen$<BR>Despite my power and beauty, I am a very innocent woman. You know? <BR>I am sure that someday, a handsome prince will come and fall in love with me. <BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Kayleen looks dreamily into the distance.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-c" mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Court Sorceress Kayleen$<BR>
You are so mean! For a woman, no matter how old she is, she is still a 17 year old girl inside that body. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Court Sorceress Kayleen$<BR>
How come you {user_class} don’t know that? <BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Kayleen looks hysterical.)</FONT><BR>
I have told you my secret dream, but I think I shouldn’t have. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-e" mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Court Sorceress Kayleen$<BR>What? Even though you know it is just a dream, it is very important. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-e" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-f" mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Court Sorceress Kayleen $<BR>
How come you {user_class} don’t know that? Everyone has a dream that isn’t realistic. People need something to depend on like a fantasy or lie. You are so cold blooded. <BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Kayleen looks hysterical.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-f" image="" itemindex="">
