   <talk_paragraph index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-g" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-h" mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Court Sorceress Kayleen$<BR>Yeah?<BR>I know it’s funny that I have a long kept dream. It’s not like I’m going to be kidnapped like a princess from a fairytale. <BR>If a Sorceress like me gets kidnapped, there will need to be at least a dozen heroes to save me. Hahaha!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-h" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-i" mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Court Sorceress Kayleen$<BR>
Yes but little dreams like this make our lives incredibly happy. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n038_royal_magician_kalaen-accepting-i" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Court Sorceress Kayleen$<BR>
I hope you remember that. Even after you become the best in the world, in order to proceed forward, you need to have another dream. Life is boring without a dream. Don’t you think so? <BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Kayleen gives a warm smile.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
